type_aliases.name: GraphZoneTraits
type_aliases.logic: Defines GraphZoneTraits as a type alias for ZoneTypeTraits, parameterized by kCompressGraphZone. This determines whether graph zone pointers are compressed or not.

type_aliases.name: ZoneNodePtr
type_aliases.logic: Defines ZoneNodePtr as a type alias for a potentially compressed pointer to a Node allocated in a zone. The compression depends on kCompressGraphZone.
